    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Demo apps showing how to use the AndroidX :graphics:graphics-shapes: library&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h1&gt;ShapesDemo&lt;/h1&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;Demo apps showing how to use the AndroidX :graphics:graphics-shapes: library&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;The View version, ShapesActivity, shows basic shape creation and morphing.&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chethaase/ShapesDemo/main/docs/images/ViewShapes.png&#34; alt=&#34;Screenshot of the View version of the app, showing some of the shapes enabled by the library&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;The Compose version of the app, ShapesAndMorphsActivity is more full-featured. It includes a shape editor:&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chethaase/ShapesDemo/main/docs/images/ComposeShapeEditor.png&#34; alt=&#34;Screenshot of the Compose version of the app, showing the shape editor&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;some other shape varieties:&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chethaase/ShapesDemo/main/docs/images/ComposeShapes.png&#34; alt=&#34;Screenshot of the Compose version of the app, showing some of the shapes enabled by the library&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;and more options for viewing and scrubbing through a morph animation.&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chethaase/ShapesDemo/main/docs/images/MorphScrub.png&#34; alt=&#34;Screenshot of morph scrubbing between two of the shapes, using the slider&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
